OL,3,CPrince Louis pictured at sea on family
OL,4,Choliday to mark eighth birthday
OL,6,FThe Prince and Princess of Wales have
OL,7,Fshared a new photo of their youngest
OL,8,Fson, Louis, on holiday in Cornwall to
OL,9,Fmark his eighth birthday.
OL,11,FPrince Louis, who shares his birthday
OL,12,Fwith William Shakespeare and St
OL,13,FGeorge's Day, is seen standing on a
OL,14,Fboat at sea during a trip to the south
OL,15,Fof England earlier this month.
OL,17,FThe picture was taken by photographer
OL,18,FMatt Porteous, who has snapped several
OL,19,Fof the Waleses' family occasions,
OL,20,Fincluding Louis' christening.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
