OL,3,CPrince Louis pictured at sea on family
OL,4,Choliday to mark eighth birthday
OL,6,FThe photo was shared on Kensington
OL,7,FPalace's social media with the
OL,8,Fcaption: "Happy birthday, Louis! 8
OL,9,Ftoday!"
OL,11,FLouis is William and Kate's youngest
OL,12,Fchild and sibling to George, 12, and
OL,13,FCharlotte, ten.
OL,15,FLouis was last seen at church with the
OL,16,Frest of the royals on Easter Sunday.
OL,18,FLouis, known for his cheeky and
OL,19,Fenergetic antics on the Buckingham
OL,20,FPalace balcony, is fourth in line to
OL,21,Fthe throne.
