OL,3,CPrince Louis pictured at sea on family
OL,4,Choliday to mark eighth birthday
OL,6,FHe was born at the private Lindo Wing
OL,7,Fof St Mary's Hospital in Paddington,
OL,8,Fin London, weighing 8lb 7oz.
OL,10,FThe young prince attends Lambrook
OL,11,FSchool, in Berkshire, close to the
OL,12,Ffamily's home in Windsor.
