OL,3,CPrince Louis pictured at sea on family
OL,4,Choliday to mark eighth birthday
OL,6,FSt George's Day is England's national
OL,7,Fday - commemorating the patron saint
OL,8,Fof England - and is annually
OL,9,Fcelebrated on April 23, often by
OL,10,Fflying the country's flag.
OL,12,FIt is also believed to be the same
OL,13,Fdate that playwright Shakespeare was
OL,14,Fboth born in 1564 and died in 1616.
